				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ai-S%C3%ADnh/poem-8zIo1kpqK4yBRE9YrLewIw">Ai Sính - 哀郢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/C%E1%BB%95-phong-k%E1%BB%B3-08-Thi%C3%AAn-t%C3%A2n-tam-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%C3%AC/poem-h4Jd-rpUD9F5lc3rtXZ3WA">Cổ phong kỳ 08 (Thiên tân tam nguyệt thì) - 古風其八（天津三月時）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/%C4%90%C3%A3ng-5/poem-TbSm6M811xlZV2bRL0RXhg">Đãng 5 - 蕩 5</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/Khu%C3%AA-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-xCNJtofKS7G-gvWpc_XOBA">Khuê từ kỳ 4 - 閨詞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/M%E1%BA%A1ch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tang/poem-0Gc_t0gCPOJk1yQzpSMuLQ">Mạch thượng tang - 陌上桑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Manh-1/poem-7bdyjCPImUljrOlYv17i3g">Manh 1 - 氓 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ph%E1%BA%A1t-m%E1%BB%99c-3/poem-kLLz1Qbo0XXDkypH1ulRSw">Phạt mộc 3 - 伐木 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/Tam-s%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%87/poem-GBmEAPjJxewHcmtMGQpBqQ">Tam sơn kệ - 三山偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/author-9I32ODUXRXPuHHWWFnp0IQ">Trần Thái Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%E1%BB%AB-C%C3%A1n/poem-TMDCykIDLkn2ovF5EJROGQ">Tặng Từ Cán - 贈徐幹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%C3%A3n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ni%C3%AAn-V%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0/poem-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Vãn đồng niên Vân Đình tiến sĩ Dương thượng thư - 輓同年雲亭進士楊尚書</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
